Package dev.siroshun.jfun.result

Interface Result<T,E>

Type Parameters:
T - the type of the success value
E - the type of the error value
All Known Subinterfaces:
Result.Failure<T,E>, Result.Success<T,E>
public sealed interface Result<T,E> permits Result.Success<T,E>, Result.Failure<T,E>
Result is a type that represents either success (Result.Success) or failure (Result.Failure).
